Step 1: Create a Kaggle Account
1. Navigate to https://www.kaggle.com/
2. Create a free account
3. Log in

Step 2: Download the Dataset
1. Visit the dataset page: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/omkarsabnis/yelp-reviews-dataset
2. Click "Download"
3. Unzip the downloaded file
4. Locate these files in the extracted folder
  - yelp_academic_dataset_review.json
  - yelp_academic_dataset_business.json

Step 3: Run the Script
1. Place the files in the appropriate folder
2. Open and run the python script: DS_4002_Project_1.ipynb
3. The notebook will filter and merge the review and business datasets
